data.description: Here's your chance to own a unique property!  This cabin-style home has the front porch of your dreams!  The home features vaulted ceilings, large fireplace with gas logs, main suite on main, another bedroom or bonus area in the loft, sitting area/nursery/office area in main suite, finished basement with full bath and kitchen, fireplace, and a cute cottage out back for hobbies or guests! This home is close to town, but sits in a private setting.
